ı\",\"title1\":\"BAP\",\"title2\":\"Tubitak\",\"title3\":\"Diğer\"}},\"SearchRakamBolumComp\":{\"title1\":\"Bilgisayar Mühendisliği\",\"title2\":\"Cerrahi Tıp Bilimleri\",\"title3\":\"Fen Bilimleri Enstitüsü\"},\"SearchRakamFakulteComp\":{\"title1\":\"Denizcilik Fakültesi\",\"title2\":\"Diş Hekimliği Fakültesi\",\"title3\":\"Fen Edebiyat Fakültesi\"}},\"tabMenu\":{\"title1\":\"ANA SAYFA\",\"title2\":\"FAKÜLTE\",\"title3\":\"BÖLÜM\",\"title4\":\"AKADEMİSYEN\"},\"UploadsContentComp\":{\"title1\":\"ÖĞRENCİ\",\"title2\":\"ÖĞRETİM GÖREVLİSİ\",\"desc\":\"Fakültemiz, Teknoloji Geliştirme Bölgesi’nde bulunuyor ve bu konum sayesinde TÜBİTAK ve özel firmaların Ar-Ge araştırma merkezleri ile Teknopark’taki şirketlerle yakın işbirliği fırsatları sunmaktadır. Bu işbirlikleri sayesinde bilimsel bilgi ve deneyimlerin sanayi sektörüne aktarılması, teknoloji geliştirme projelerinin yürütülmesi ve öğrencilere staj fırsatları sağlanmaktadır. Mezunlarımız, hem kamu kurumlarında hem de özel sektörde mühendislik alanında iş bulabilirler ve kendi işletmelerini kurma fırsatına sahiptirler.\"}},\"sayfalarPage\":{\"title\":\"Sayfalar\",\"title2\":\"Dosyalar\",\"title3\":\"Bağlantılar\"},\"OrganizasyonSemasi\":{\"title\":\"Organizasyon Şeması\"},\"YonetimPage\":{\"title\":\"Rektör\",\"titledanisman\":\"Rektör Danışmanları\",\"titleyardimci\":\"Rektör Yardımcıları\",\"rector\":{\"title\":\"Rektör\",\"alias\":\"REKTÖR\",\"title2\":\"Eğitim Hayatı\",\"title3\":\"Bilimsel Yayınlar\",\"title4\":\"Kitaplar\",\"title5\":\"Akademik ve İdari Görevler\",\"title6\":\"Üyesi Olduğu Ulusal ve Uluslararası Kuruluşlar\",\"title7\":\" Görev Tanımı\",\"contentGorevt\":\"$10\",\"yardim\":\"$11\",\"yardim3\":\"$12\",\"yardim4\":\"$13\",\"yardim2\":\"$14\"},\"title2\":\"Rektör Yardımcıları\",\"desc2\":\"Rektör Yardımcısı\",\"yonetim1\":\"Yönetim\",\"yonetim2\":\"Eğitim - Öğretim\",\"yonetim3\":\"Araştırma - Geliştirme / Toplumsal Katkı\",\"title3\":\"Rektör Danışmanları\",\"desc3\":\"Rektör Danışmanı\",\"danisman1\":\"Yerel Yönetimler ve Kamu Kurumları İlişkileri\",\"danisman2\":\"Üniversite-Sanayi İşbirliği\"},\"eventsComponent\":{\"title\":\"Etkinlikler\",\"noEventTitle\":\"Etkinlik Bulunmamaktadır.\"},\"announcementsComponent\":{\"title\":\"Duyurular\",\"noAnnouncementsTitle\":\"Duyuru Bulunmamaktadır.\",\"badge\":\"Öğrenci İşleri\"},\"rectorComponent\":{\"title1\":\"Umutla Başlayan, Üretimle Büyüyen, \",\"title2\":\" Aday Araştırma Üniversitesi;\",\"title3\":\" Kocaeli Üniversitesi!\",\"alias\":\"REKTÖRÜMÜZ\"},\"counterComponent\":{\"title\":\"Sayılarla KOÜ\"},\"poppageComponent\":{\"title1\":\"Bağlantılar\",\"title2\":\"Dökümanlar\",\"dnsa\":\"Tekrar Gösterme\"},\"footerComponent\":{\"slogan\":\"Eğitimde Çağdaş, Sağlıkta Güçlü, Bilimde Öncü Üniversite\",\"contact\":\"İletişim\"},\"personalCardComponent\":{\"moreDetailsButton\":\"Ayrıntılı Bilgi\"},\"months\":{\"short\":{\"jan\":\"Oca\",\"feb\":\"Şub\",\"mar\":\"Mar\",\"ape\":\"Nis\",\"may\":\"May\",\"jun\":\"Haz\",\"jul\":\"Tem\",\"aug\":\"Ağu\",\"sep\":\"Eyl\",\"oct\":\"Eki\",\"nov\":\"Kas\",\"dec\":\"Ara\"},\"long\":{\"jan\":\"OCAK\",\"feb\":\"ŞUBAT\",\"mar\":\"MART\",\"ape\":\"NİSAN\",\"may\":\"MAYIS\",\"jun\":\"HAZİRAN\",\"jul\":\"TEMMUZ\",\"aug\":\"AĞUSTOS\",\"sep\":\"EYLÜL\",\"oct\":\"EKİM\",\"nov\":\"KASIM\",\"dec\":\"ARALIK\"}},\"asideComp\":{\"title\":\"KOU İNTERAKTİF\",\"searchList\":{\"1\":\"Online hizmetlerde ara...\",\"2\":\"Akademik Takvim\",\"3\":\"Online işlemler\",\"4\":\"Duyurular\"}},\"FacTabBoxGridComp\":{\"title1\":\"AKADEMIK PERSONEL\",\"title2\":\"İDARI PERSONEL\",\"title3\":\"ÖĞRENCI SAYISI\",\"title4\":\"DERSLIK SAYISI\",\"title5\":\"LABORATUVAR SAYISI\"},\"PersonelDetailCounterComp\":{\"strong\":\"Kurum Bilgileri: \",\"detailButton\":\"Detay\"},\"ProgressBarBoxComp\":{\"title\":\"Öğrenci\"},\"agenda\":\"Gündem\",\"news\":\"Haberler\",\"allButton\":\"tümü\",\"beforeButton\":\"Önceki\",\"afterButton\":\"Sonraki\"}},\"en\":{\"main\":{\"lang\":\"en\",\"home\":{\"title1\":\"For a Quarter Century\",\"titleSwipe1\":\"ART\",\"titleSwipe2\":\"SCIENCE\",\"titleSwipe3\":\"TECHNOLOGY\",\"titleSwipe4\":\"FUTURE\",\"titleSwipe5\":\"SPORTS\",\"title2\":\"is born here.\",\"subTitle1\":\"We educate, research, and produce\",\"subTitle2\":\"for our Turkey.\",\"swipe\":\"Swipe Down\",\"slideText1\":\"From Our University\",\"slideText2\":\"IMPORTANT UPDATES\",\"newsTitle\":\"News\",\"sloganTitle1\":\" INNOVATIVE AND LEADING\",\"sloganTitle2\":\" UNIVERSITY\",\"sloganText\":\"As a university in an industrial city, with our pioneering role in collaboration with industry and our internationally respected R\u0026D efforts, we act with a consciousness of sustainability in all the activities we carry out, transforming our society, region, country, and the world.\"},\"announcementsPage\":{\"title\":\"Announcements\",\"subTitle\":\"Current Announcements\",\"noAnnouncementsTitle\":\"No Announcements Found.\",\"searchInput\":\"Search Announcements...\",\"sidebarListTitle\":\"All Announcements\",\"sidebarListYear\":\"Year\"},\"eventsPage\":{\"title\":\"Events\",\"searchInput\":\"Search...\",\"detailButton\":\"Detail\",\"sidebarListTitle\":\"All Events\",\"sidebarCategoriesTitle\":\"Categories\"},\"genSecPage\":{\"title\":\"Secretariat General\",\"aboutUsTitle\":\"About Us\",\"aboutUs\":\"As the head of the administrative organization of Kocaeli University, the Secretary General is responsible for the performance and control of all administrative duties to the Rectorate; ensuring the efficient, orderly, and harmonious operation of units within the university administrative organization, and fulfilling the duties in accordance with relevant laws and regulations, as well as decisions of the board of directors and senate. To assist the General Secretary in carrying out the duties mentioned above, two Deputy General Secretaries serve.\"},\"newsPage\":{\"title\":\"News\",\"detailsPage\":{\"title\":\"News Details\"}},\"aboutUsPage\":{\"title\":\"About Us\",\"descs\":{\"title1\":\"A QUARTER-CENTURY SCIENCE NEST\",\"desc1\":\"With advancing technology, we offer both our city and our students the opportunity to be a part of this development. With scientific and technological advancements, our country is confidently moving towards the future. We are determined to be an important part of Turkey, which produces and develops. Kocaeli University Technopark exports to many countries. The countries to which Kocaeli University exports include the USA, Germany, Azerbaijan, Spain, Switzerland, Russia, Georgia, Kenya, TRNC, Saudi Arabia, Syria, and Greece. Our Technopark, which will be further strengthened with newly built offices and companies covering 40,000 square meters of closed space through tenders, will play a leading role in the production of high value-added products needed by our country, and in the development of its technology.\",\"title2\":\"A SPECTACULAR CAMPUS\",\"desc2\":\"August 17, 1999, is a painful date for both our country and our university, with great losses due to the devastating Marmara earthquake. The effect of this great destruction caused the disappearance of 75% of our university, but our University rapidly healed this great wound with its strength and reached its modern and highly developed campus used at present.\",\"desc22\":\"The Umuttepe Campus, Turkey's first specially-designed campus, is one of Turkey's and the world's distinguished campuses. Located at the heart of nature, away from the noise of the city, our campus has a special location with its refreshing air. Our campus, which is a source of pride with its sports facilities, research and application hospital, modern educational institutions, and social areas, is a remarkable facility.\",\"title3\":\"TODAY'S KOCAELİ UNIVERSITY\",\"desc3\":\"It is a giant educational institution serving with 19 Faculties, 3 Colleges, 16 Vocational Schools, 4 Graduate Schools, and 1 State Conservatory. As of 2022, our university,with its 67,250 students, which educates individuals for our country every year, has an important position in our country's research and development (R\u0026D) activities with 24 Research and Application Centers/Units. It ranks first among student activities with 119 Student Clubs and Societies, and through its clubs, it carries out social responsibility activities and social and cultural events.\",\"title4\":\"A WORLD UNIVERSITY\",\"desc4\":\"$15\",\"title5\":\"SOCIAL, SPORTS AND DISABLED-FRIENDLY UNIVERSITY\",\"desc5\":\"$16\",\"title6\":\"LIFELONG EDUCATION\",\"desc6\":\"$17\",\"title7\":\"TECHNOPARK\",\"desc7\":\"With developing technology, as a university, we offer both our city and our students the opportunity to be involved in this development. Our country is taking firm steps towards the future with scientific and technological developments. We are determinedly walking towards becoming an important part of our productive and developing Turkey. Kocaeli University Technopark exports to many countries. The leading export countries are the USA, Germany, Azerbaijan, Spain, Switzerland, Russia, Georgia, Kenya, TRNC, S. Arabia, Syria and Greece. Our Technopark, which will be further strengthened with new offices and companies that have been tendered and will serve with a closed area of 40,000 square meters, will play a leading role in the production of high value-added products and the development of technology that our country needs.\",\"list\":{\"title\":\"BASICS\",\"item1\":\"Over 67,000 students\",\"item2\":\"Over 2000 Academic Staff\",\"item3\":\"19 Faculties\",\"item4\":\"3 Vocational Schools\",\"item5\":\"16 Vocational Colleges\",\"item6\":\"4 Graduate Schools\",\"item7\":\"24 Research and Application Centers/Units\",\"item8\":\"As of 2022, more than 1500 students from 84 countries have come to our university for bahclor education.\",\"item9\":\"Our library provides access to a total of 121,397 printed books, 485,145 e-books, 1,097 printed journals, 66,917 e-journals, 4,824 printed theses, and 2,626,479 e-theses from 146 databases.\",\"item10\":\"Different companies from various sectors operate and conduct their activities within the Technopark.\",\"item11\":\"The radio station 'Radyo Ki' within the Faculty of Communication broadcasts over the internet and on the 94.8 FM frequency band.\",\"item12\":\"Kocaeli University Application and Research Television (KOU TV), which started broadcasting in 2015, reflects important scientific activities as well as cultural, artistic, and sports activities carried out by various units of our university.\"}}},\"404Page\":{\"title\":\"404 - Page Not Found\",\"desc\":\"Sorry, the page you are looking for could not be found.\"},\"contactPage\":{\"title\":\"Contact\"},\"collaborationsPage\":{\"title\":\"Our Collaborations\",\"list\":{\"1\":{\"desc\":\"Arçelik Inc.: Starting employment-focused remote R\u0026D activities, Arçelik collaborated with Kocaeli University to implement a project (in March 2021) targeting students studying in the field of software. In the project called Prep, participating students will continue their university education while remotely contributing to software projects at Arçelik. With the Prep project, Arçelik aims to support the software sector in Turkey, bring out young talents in our universities, and pioneer them to contribute to our country's economy and production.\"}}},\"employeePage\":{\"title\":\"Employees\"},\"countsPage\":{\"title\":\"Academic Staff\",\"title2\":\"Academic Publications\",\"title3\":\"Student Exchange Programs\",\"title4\":\"Scholarships for Students\",\"title5\":\"Library\",\"title6\":\"Awards of Our University\",\"title7\":\"Number of students and their distribution\",\"AcademicPublicationsComp\":{\"title\":\"Conference Paper\",\"title2\":\"Academic Article\",\"title3\":\"Chapter in a Book\",\"title4\":\"Book\",\"title5\":\"Academic Publication\"},\"ProgramDagilimContentComp\":{\"title\":\"Number and Distribution of Programs\",\"desc\":\"Kocaeli University has a total of 63,886 students in the 2022-2023 academic year. The university can be evaluated under three main headings: academic units, academic staff, and students. Academic units include faculties, graduate schools, schools, and vocational schools. A total of 25 academic units offer bahclor, associate, master's, and doctoral education, but exact numbers are not specified.\"},\"StudentContentComp\":{\"title\":\"Numeric Distribution of Students\",\"desc1\":\"Numeric information regarding\",\"desc2\":\"our students\"},\"DegisimProgramlariComp\":{\"desc\":\"Numeric information about students studying at our university in 2024\",\"title1\":\"Bachelor\",\"title2\":\"Master's\",\"title3\":\"Doctorate\"},\"DegisimProgramlariRightComp\":{\"title1\":\"Mevlana Program\",\"title2\":\"Erasmus Program\",\"title3\":\"Farabi Program\",\"go\":\"Outgoing Student\",\"come\":\"Incoming Student\"},\"BurslarComp\":{\"title1\":\"KOCAELİ UNIVERSITY FOUNDATION SCHOLARSHIP\",\"title2\":\"KOCAELİ UNIVERSITY SCHOLARSHIP FOR FOOD SERVICE\",\"desc\":\"We have increased the number of housing, scholarship, and free meal services provided to financially disadvantaged students, reaching more students with these opportunities. The scholarship amounts given to our students were increased in 2023.\"},\"BilimselArastirmaComp\":{\"title\":\"Scientific Research Projects\",\"ListPrgImg\":{\"title\":\"PROJECT\",\"text\":\"TOTAL ALLOCATION\"},\"ListParagraphs\":{\"title1\":\"TÜBİTAK Project\",\"title2\":\"Externally Funded Project\",\"title3\":\"National Project\",\"title4\":\"International Project\",\"title5\":\"BAP Project\"}},\"SosyalImkanlarComp\":{\"title\":\"Social Opportunities\",\"grid\":{\"1\":{\"title\":\"Student Clubs\",\"label\":\"Club\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"Health Service\",\"label\":\"Area\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Foundation Scholarship\",\"label\":\"Student\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"Meal Scholarship\",\"label\":\"Student\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Sports Facilities\",\"label\":\"Area\"}}},\"PhysicallyContentsComp\":{\"title\":\"Physical Facilit